类 CompileStates

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<Env<AttrContext>,CompileStates.CompileState>

    public class CompileStates
extends java.util.HashMap<Env<AttrContext>,CompileStates.CompileState>
    Partial map to record which compiler phases have been executed for each compilation unit. Used for ATTR and FLOW phases.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.
